        <updateDate>2019-08-21T21:08:29Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Open America's Waters Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill eliminates restrictions on coastwise trade under the Jones Act, which governs domestic transportation of merchandise or passengers by vessels.</p> <p>The bill directs the U.S. Coast Guard to issue regulations that require all vessels permitted to engage in coastwise trade to meet all appropriate safety and security requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
